{{Top|leg}}
The '''Great Bantha Breakfast Biscuit Run''' was established between the [[Planet/Legends|planets]] [[Sullust/Legends|Sullust]] and [[Gastrula]] by the [[Sullustan/Legends|Sullustan]] [[Bungo Bung]]. For two weeks, Captain Bung transported large amounts of [[Bantha Breakfast Biscuit]]s from Sullust to Gastrula, making several thousand [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]]. The run was ended, however, when it was discovered that the biscuits were mutating into [[Giant Amorphous Bantha Breakfast Biscuit]]s.

